# 🎯 Depth Pro - AI Depth Map Generator

Transform any 2D image into a detailed 3D depth map using Apple's state-of-the-art **Depth Pro** model!

## ✨ Features

- 🚀 **Ultra-fast**: Generate depth maps in ~0.3 seconds
- 🎯 **High accuracy**: Sharp boundary detection and fine details  
- 🌐 **Universal**: Works with any image - no camera metadata needed
- 🆓 **Free**: No usage limits, registration, or API keys required
- ⚡ **Real-time**: GPU-accelerated processing

## 🔬 How It Works

This space uses Apple's open-source [Depth Pro](https://github.com/apple/ml-depth-pro) model, which represents a breakthrough in monocular depth estimation. The model:

- Predicts **metric depth** with absolute scale
- Achieves **exceptional sharpness** in depth boundaries  
- Estimates **focal length** automatically
- Processes **2.25MP images** in 0.3 seconds

## 🎮 How to Use

1. **Upload** any image (photos of people, objects, landscapes work great!)
2. **Wait** ~0.3 seconds for processing  
3. **Download** your depth maps:
   - **Colored version**: Great for visualization
   - **Grayscale version**: Perfect for 3D reconstruction

## 🔧 Applications

- **3D Photography**: Create depth-aware photo effects
- **AR/VR**: Spatial understanding for virtual objects
- **Robotics**: Navigation and object manipulation  
- **Film/Gaming**: 3D scene reconstruction
- **Research**: Computer vision and depth analysis

## 📖 Research

Based on the paper: *"Depth Pro: Sharp Monocular Metric Depth in Less Than a Second"* by Aleksei Bochkovskii, Amaël Delaunoy, Hugo Germain, Marcel Santos, Yichao Zhou, Stephan R. Richter, and Vladlen Koltun.

## 🤝 Credits

- **Model**: [Apple ML Research](https://github.com/apple/ml-depth-pro)
- **Interface**: Built with [Gradio](https://gradio.app/)  
